author: cmpilato
msg: Switch order of the 'fs'/'repos' and 'lock' parameters of
svn_fs_attach_lock() and svn_repos_fs_attach_lock() to comply with
(svn_fs_attach_lock): Tweak order of params to make 'fs' first.
(svn_repos_fs_attach_lock): Tweak order of params to make 'fs' first.
(fs_vtable_t): Tweak param order in 'attach_lock' vtable function.
(svn_fs_fs__attach_lock): Tweak order of params to make 'fs' first.
(svn_fs_base__attach_lock): Tweak order of params to make 'fs' first.

author: julianfoad
msg: Fix issue #2214: poor error message when intermediate dir missing in copy.
Improve the error message, and also add a test for this behaviour.
(open_directory): Replace "out of date" error with "path not present" error.
(url_to_non_existent_url_path): New test to ensure that 'svn copy' fails when
one of the destination URL path components does not exist.
